Package chat.model

Class Chatbot

java.lang.Object
chat.model.Chatbot
public class Chatbot
extends java.lang.Object
This a crude chatbot. It takes user response and responds with what the user says. It can respond to some questions.
Author:
Jay Clegg

    • quiet

      public java.lang.String quiet()
      Checks if the user hasn't responded multiple times. If they haven't, it asks them to talk. Called by processText().
      Returns:
      Nothing if the user sends a message, or a message requesting the user to talk to the chatbot if they haven't.
